<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-textfield.xml">TextField</db:link> is a single line text editor. <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-textfield.xml">TextField</db:link> extends <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-textinput.xml">TextInput</db:link> with a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-textfield.xml#placeholderText-prop">placeholder text</db:link> functionality, and adds decoration.</db:para>
